title: We Got Married
author: Aaron Burriss
description:
Part 1: Asking Her To Be My Girlfriend-  https://youtu.be/BKHur5DQ3gw
Part 2: I Proposed- https://youtu.be/0BYobDZutZY

When I met Veronica Merrell 4 and a half years ago I already knew I wanted to marry this girl. So on September 30, 2021 I dropped on one knee and asked her to marry me and  on December 27th 2021 we said "I do". I can't wait to spend the rest of my life with you Veronica and I can't wait to see what this new year has in store for us! I love you Roni! üíú
